name: Nabinagar Government  Cellage
details: College Location: Nabinagar,Brahmanbaria. Government/Non-Government: Government ; Year of Establishment: 1969
research: Nabinagar is an ancient aesthetic township, proud of education, art-literature and cultural heritage cherished by Titus Meghna. Nabinagar Government College is the only government higher education institution located in Nabinagar Upazila Sadar. The institution has been imparting the light of knowledge to the students of Bhati region for ages, embodying the spirit of regional identity and the great liberation war. The institution is proud of the walk of elite people and the creation of famous personalities.
